{"tid":906307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[露餡] 車cam影住3人持鐵鎚窮追死者 目擊者嘆太衝動","createTime":"2018-11-18T00:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T05:55:37.000Z","uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4d105715c0e9c24cec08f977f7134068cda3831c","tid":906307,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T00:50:13.000Z","msg":"車cam影住3人持鐵鎚窮追死者 目擊者嘆太衝動<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923875\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923875&d=xfmZOGnpSnlsLVliURnZaUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=fefbbf01\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181117%2F58923875&h=ac4a04fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181117/58923875</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542422562_e61a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542422562_e61a.jpg&h=5bab3853&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨晚沙田大圍一間車房的GTR被3名男子扑爆大銀幕，車房老闆與職員發現後追打其中1名涉刑毀男子，結果刑毀男被人按地毆斃。《蘋果》獲得讀者Anson提供一段當時疑為事件中死者扑玻璃後，遭車房老闆及職員追趕的片段，Anson表示，昨晚約6時，他駕車載同女友，將車停在成全路後，兩人在車廂商討食晚飯的地方，其間突然見到一名穿白衣牛仔褲的男子，由路中心走出，在其司機位旁邊走過，當時白衣男還手持木棍，他女友還問「做乜嘢揸木棍？」Anson估計「打架啩」，豈料隔4秒後，便見到左面行人路，一名穿深色上衣的男子急步跑往白衣男方向。<br />\n<br />\nAnson憶述當時情況指深色上衣男子後面，再有另一名男子持鐵鎚尾隨，其後還有一名穿灰色衫的男子亦跟隨在後，「三個人係一夥，好似搵緊人，向住白衣男方向急步行，我覺得好奇，但冇理由追上去，好危險。」<br />\n<br />\nAnson稍後看新聞才知發生兇殺案，回想起車cam影到的四名男子，懷疑當時首先跑過其車身邊手持木棍的是死者，而三名大漢疑是追趕死者的兇徒。「我希望將片段交畀警方，睇吓幫唔幫到忙，盡下責任。」由於他見到其中一名追趕的男子手持鐵鎚，但警方講述案情時未有透露找到鐵鎚等兇器，所以希望藉此提供一些線索予警方調查。「好似話死者太陽穴凹咗，腳踢未必凹，懷疑用鎚仔扑。」<br />\n<br />\n對於死者被人按地制服仍不斷被毆，Anson坦言有人情緒太高漲，「唔可以冷靜啲，都撳住佢，都咁傷，走得去邊，3個人仲咁大力撳住佢，攞命！我覺得其實唔使搞得咁嚴重，唔夠理性。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421493_1650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421493_1650.jpg&h=4c9d36c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白衣男疑為死者手持木棍由路中心走出，懷疑當時他已扑爛私家車玻璃後逃走。（讀者Anson提供)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421493_776a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421493_776a.jpg&h=ebeb5828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n白衣男疑為死者手持木棍由路中心走出，懷疑當時他已扑爛私家車玻璃後逃走。（讀者Anson提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421508_e159.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421508_e159.jpg&h=890d0337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n稍後穿深色衫男子在行人路急步追趕而至。（讀者Anson提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421508_47e7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421508_47e7.jpg&h=5afb22d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一名黑衫男手持鐵鎚尾隨。（讀者Anson提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421520_f784.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421520_f784.jpg&h=ccd6f037&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再有一名灰色衫男子跟隨兩人急步走向白衣男方向。（讀者Anson提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181117/large/1542421520_1d74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181117%2Flarge%2F1542421520_1d74.jpg&h=10c9ca0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（讀者Anson提供）"},{"pid":"2216174a3f0a3bf0889eb58f9268310108a04167","tid":906307,"uid":167506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T05:55:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}